					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you'd count a Genesis with the MegaCD and 32X add-ons attached as one system, then you'd have two 68000s, two SH2s and a Z80. Plus three graphics processors and four audio chips.
<br />
<br />Other than that, I guess the Saturn is the most complicated game console I've come across in terms of number of processors.</div>

